{"tid":2457094,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4] Fifa21 Pro club 隊招人，主打控傳配合","createTime":"2021-03-22T11:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T16:37:59.000Z","uid":19126,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"91bd126048ef7ffc57c7100a079c9b95acb00cf4","tid":2457094,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T11:17:22.000Z","msg":"介紹下自己先<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩個人既隊重建中，打到第十一季，好好彩拎左d1 title，依家想招隊友一齊玩，唔打算報比賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n目標都係留係d1，間唔中爭下title咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡介如下 : <br />\n我地都知自己腳法差，唔識過人，所以主打控傳，不吝嗇橫傳回傳，節奏可能比較緩慢，睇準先向前走位/放直線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講就係靠走位同配合，多過個人突破<br />\n<br />\n盡量少L1三角，因為難傳亦難控<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地想招有同樣諗法或願意配合既隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前鋒 : 以識走直線位為主，唔好靜係識拉邊，在危險地帶要可以盡量做正確決定（射、造就隊友、回傳、個人突破等等）<br />\n<br />\n翼 : 以肯走位出波為主，最好能夠適量協防（唔洗入中路守）<br />\n<br />\n防中 : 以堅守位置為主，目前人少，不太建議b2b防中，簡單控球傳球就可以<br />\n<br />\n歡迎新手，以肯配合戰術同團隊精神為重點，同埋唔好亂call波死call波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好可能會逐個逐個試，十分抱歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似好多要求，但因為控球打法只要有一個隊友唔跟，就會散哂，所以唯有先小人後君子，實在好抱歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既朋友仔麻煩你留tg，我會盡快聯絡你架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f12d0b8235c1f9f5b2a415b8ebf5b1c8fc8c18f8","tid":2457094,"uid":172999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T14:07:19.000Z","msg":"踢開邊線 翼閘都得 偽9號及逗住型防中也可<br />\n<br />\n本身有踢開D1閘位<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6db9729e5866d3f9dd7f3cf922faf98f63b845","tid":2457094,"uid":33673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T14:19:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/GloryGloryHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FGloryGloryHK&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXF3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=da9ae00e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/GloryGloryHK</a>"},{"pid":"83eab15fc6bed0b5154827f79eb16eecfe0a3dc4","tid":2457094,"uid":15381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T14:39:16.000Z","msg":"中場/翼<br />\n其他位都可以試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c97413803fd6cf665a0b644c031699668bf1232","tid":2457094,"uid":61678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T14:54:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/bigpepee\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fbigpepee&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXF3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=3a65add0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/bigpepee</a>"},{"pid":"e234fc92204285f79ac0f53254cc2fe36ae88329","tid":2457094,"uid":125854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T15:47:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/utcoins1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Futcoins1&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXF3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=c1cf557a\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/utcoins1</a>"},{"pid":"6476e947be38caa8755d402bc3d167b5412c33ab","tid":2457094,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T19:30:35.000Z","msg":"會聯絡大家的，放心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c712619f0227cf04c1458d096b4a35a92b9862","tid":2457094,"uid":208017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T06:20:53.000Z","msg":"真pro club新手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/nor